Logika
This game is a genre logic arcade game

###### Launching ######

1) OS GNU/Linux:
  a) install library pygame (available in repositories of popular GNU/Linux distributions)
  б) double clicking the left mouse button to run file logika.py or running the command in terminal: python logika.py

2) OS Windows
  a) install language Python 2.7 (https://www.python.org/downloads/windows/)
  б) install library pygame (http://pygame.org/download.shtml)
  в) double clicking the left mouse button to run file logika.py

3) ОS OS X:
  *Not tested*
  The principle of the installation is the same as in the case of Windows (see above)

###### Introduction ######

You employee space ship. During the long flight on Board was discovered an unknown subject.
According to preliminary data the detonator. You are entrusted with the task to unlock it! Good luck!!!

###### Rules ######

You have is 10 colored blocks. You need to choose 4 blocks and arrange them in a line.
Just only 8 lines. Your target is to unravel a coded sequence of blocks.
Gamma will tell how many blocks you selected the right colors and standing in his place.
Omega will tell how many blocks you select the correct color but not standing in his place.

